<lb n="0239a19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note n="0239002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0239003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宮】</note><app n="0239003"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">經一卷</rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0239a20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0239a21" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0239004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失譯…漢錄＝漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，漢失譯師名【明】</note><note n="0239004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">失譯…漢錄＝漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，＝漢失譯師名【明】</note><app n="0239004" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">失譯人名在後漢錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">漢失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">漢失譯師名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0239a22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><lg xml:id="lgT15p0239a2201"><l>一切一其心，</l><l>皆聽美言訓，</l>
<lb n="0239a23" ed="T"/><l>佛所<note n="0239005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝行【宮】</note><app n="0239005"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">行</rdg></app>得道，</l><l>且聽我彼經。</l>
<lb n="0239a24" ed="T"/><l>彼空亦不斷，</l><l>有行皆非常，</l>
<lb n="0239a25" ed="T"/><l>夫行不敗壞，</l><l>佛以講授經。</l>
<lb n="0239a26" ed="T"/><l>深微難見事，</l><l>非章原之句，</l>
<lb n="0239a27" ed="T"/><l>通彼能敷演，</l><l>是以故為師。</l>
<lb n="0239a28" ed="T"/><l>從本以存本，</l><l>有造法之積，</l>
<lb n="0239a29" ed="T"/><l>從慧以除棄，</l><l>上士所講說。</l>
<pb n="0239b" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0239b"/>
<lb n="0239b01" ed="T"/><l>所從因緣有，</l><l>有行皆無有，</l>
<lb n="0239b02" ed="T"/><l>亦有前世<note n="0239006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝除【元】【明】</note><app n="0239006"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><!--CBETA todo type: None-->除</rdg></app>，</l><l>無知彼諸行；</l>
<lb n="0239b03" ed="T"/><l>亦如欲演身，</l><l>日親之所講，</l>
<lb n="0239b04" ed="T"/><l><note n="0239007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝夫【三】，大災＝夫裁【宮】</note><note n="0239007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大災＝夫裁【宮】，大＝夫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0239007"><lem wit="【大】">大災</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">夫裁</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">夫災</rdg></app>患無數，</l><l>皆以歸流身。</l>
<lb n="0239b05" ed="T"/><l>刪定如本文，</l><l>所演眾要言，</l>
<lb n="0239b06" ed="T"/><l>靡麗五字句，</l><l>明誓以勸勉。</l>
<lb n="0239b07" ed="T"/><l>以頌文具足，</l><l>偶字音商備，</l>
<lb n="0239b08" ed="T"/><l>若花實雜<note n="0239008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糅＝采【宮】</note><app n="0239008"><lem wit="【大】">糅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">采</rdg></app>，</l><l>皆聽彼我誨。</l>
<lb n="0239b09" ed="T"/><l>身非人非命，</l><l>不丈夫非士，</l>
<lb n="0239b10" ed="T"/><l>若體若<note n="0239009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239009"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有</rdg></app>艶，</l><l>斯事都無彼。</l>
<lb n="0239b11" ed="T"/><l>夫身造而有，</l><l>以有即敗亡，</l>
<lb n="0239b12" ed="T"/><l>無強皆歸<note n="0239010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝終【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命＝終【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239010"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">終</rdg></app>，</l><l>如沫蹈踐碎；</l>
<lb n="0239b13" ed="T"/><l>無強則無常，</l><l>無常即無樂；</l>
<lb n="0239b14" ed="T"/><l>無常亦為苦，</l><l>非身身非我；</l>
<lb n="0239b15" ed="T"/><l>身非常亦苦，</l><l>非彼應為身。</l>
<lb n="0239b16" ed="T"/><l><note n="0239011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝苦【宮】</note><app n="0239011"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">苦</rdg></app>體艶我有，</l><l>身都無可有；</l>
<lb n="0239b17" ed="T"/><l>若以都無體，</l><l>有存亦有亡。</l>
<lb n="0239b18" ed="T"/><l>慧者以本末，</l><l>何彼已有體？</l>
<lb n="0239b19" ed="T"/><l>若以無<note n="0239012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝生【宮】</note><app n="0239012"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">生</rdg></app>者，</l><l>不得以自由，</l>
<lb n="0239b20" ed="T"/><l>有校計若此，</l><l>何彼體我有？</l>
<lb n="0239b21" ed="T"/><l>斯體身為空，</l><l>體我有為虛，</l>
<lb n="0239b22" ed="T"/><l>應因緣為有，</l><l>非身逝心造，</l>
<lb n="0239b23" ed="T"/><l>非眾人身造，</l><l>亦非自身造，</l>
<lb n="0239b24" ed="T"/><l>都無<note n="0239013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身有＝有身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身有＝有身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239013"><lem wit="【大】">身有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有身</rdg></app>造，</l><l>亦身<note n="0239014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無不＝不無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無不＝不無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239014"><lem wit="【大】">無不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不無</rdg></app>造。</l>
<lb n="0239b25" ed="T"/><l>以身無造者，</l><l>從彼為得諦。</l>
<lb n="0239b26" ed="T"/><l>亦非都骨節，</l>
<lb n="0239b27" ed="T"/><l>從前世方來，</l><l>亦非天造身，</l>
<lb n="0239b28" ed="T"/><l>非神所化<note n="0239015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">城＝成【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">城＝成【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239015"><lem wit="【大】">城</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">成</rdg></app>，</l><l>非無行無本，</l>
<lb n="0239b29" ed="T"/><l>無因為自有，</l><l>是身有所由，</l>
<pb n="0239c" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0239c"/>
<lb n="0239c01" ed="T"/><l>有事亦有<note n="0239016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝初【宮】</note><app n="0239016"><lem wit="【大】">物</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">初</rdg></app>。</l><l>有本有所起，</l>
<lb n="0239c02" ed="T"/><l>稍稍為生有，</l><l>本以癡亦愛，</l>
<lb n="0239c03" ed="T"/><l>心與愛有漏，</l><l>亦有縛亦結，</l>
<lb n="0239c04" ed="T"/><l>行二品為漏。</l><l>斯為本亦餘，</l>
<lb n="0239c05" ed="T"/><l>世與受因緣，</l><l>以由彼斯身，</l>
<lb n="0239c06" ed="T"/><l>以漸能致有。</l><l>初<note n="0239017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">始＝如【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">始＝如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239017"><lem wit="【大】">始</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如</rdg></app>有精沫，</l>
<lb n="0239c07" ed="T"/><l>精沫為轉凝，</l><l>足為生<note n="0239018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兩＝雨【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩＝雨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0239c08" ed="T"/><l>以<app type="star" corresp="#0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app>為轉厚，</l><l>以序有四體，</l>
<lb n="0239c09" ed="T"/><l>為生頭第五，</l><l>若干骨積聚，</l>
<lb n="0239c10" ed="T"/><l>從行為用成，</l><l>頭九為髑髏，</l>
<lb n="0239c11" ed="T"/><l>頞䪼為二骨，</l><l>齒根三十二，</l>
<lb n="0239c12" ed="T"/><l>齒三十二骨，</l><l>頸為與<note n="0239019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239019"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>本，</l>
<lb n="0239c13" ed="T"/><l>鼻為與上腭，</l><l>心與頸嚨喉，</l>
<lb n="0239c14" ed="T"/><l>凡為骨<note n="0239020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八十＝十八【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八十＝十八【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239020"><lem wit="【大】">八十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十八</rdg></app>。</l><l>頰車與頸四，</l>
<lb n="0239c15" ed="T"/><l>咽亦為骨四，</l><l>左臂與右臂，</l>
<lb n="0239c16" ed="T"/><l>凡有骨五十。</l><l>若其斯左脇，</l>
<lb n="0239c17" ed="T"/><l>應有十三肋；</l><l>亦斯右脇然，</l>
<lb n="0239c18" ed="T"/><l>應有肋十三，</l><l>斯為四十八。</l>
<lb n="0239c19" ed="T"/><l>三三三相連，</l><l>二為二相連，</l>
<lb n="0239c20" ed="T"/><l>其餘不相連，</l><l>身者以為<note n="0239021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彊＝疆【明】＊</note><note n="0239021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->彊＝疆【明】＊</note><app n="0239021"><lem wit="【大】">彊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">疆</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0239c21" ed="T"/><l>如束葦無彊，</l><l>脊膂三十二，</l>
<lb n="0239c22" ed="T"/><l>尻與腰為三，</l><l>若其斯左<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】【磧砂】" resp="CBETA.maha">髀<note type="cf1">K30n1011_p0344c20</note><note type="cf2">Q28_p0290b23</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">脾</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0239c23" ed="T"/><l>骨為二十五；</l><l>右髀為亦然，</l>
<lb n="0239c24" ed="T"/><l>為骨二十五；</l><l>肩<note n="0239022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髀＝　【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髀＝<space quantity="1" unit="chars"/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>髀有骨四，</l>
<lb n="0239c25" ed="T"/><l>凡三百二十。</l><l>敷演<note n="0239023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝各【宮】</note><app n="0239023"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">各</rdg></app>之諦，</l>
<lb n="0239c26" ed="T"/><l>佛以日斷嗣，</l><l>彼叚悉以聚，</l>
<lb n="0239c27" ed="T"/><l>諸根<note n="0239024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為以＝以為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為以＝以為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239024"><lem wit="【大】">為以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以為</rdg></app>縫，</l><l>非瘡而裹之，</l>
<lb n="0239c28" ed="T"/><l>肉血以塗<note n="0239025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𢴉＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𢴉＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239025"><lem wit="【大】">𢴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>，</l><l>如木機關縷，</l>
<lb n="0239c29" ed="T"/><l>為如幻師幻。</l><l>骨機關亦然，</l>
<pb n="0240a" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0240a"/>
<lb n="0240a01" ed="T"/><l>以筋纏縛成，</l><l>合聚骨若此，</l>
<lb n="0240a02" ed="T"/><l>以為是形體。</l><l>愚者莫不著，</l>
<lb n="0240a03" ed="T"/><l>智者而不著。</l><l>生革以隱蔽，</l>
<lb n="0240a04" ed="T"/><l>九孔為大瘡，</l><l>周匝為滲漏，</l>
<lb n="0240a05" ed="T"/><l>不淨腐臭處，</l><l>口<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">喙<note type="cf1">K30n1011_p0345a05</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">啄</rdg></app>如為孔，</l>
<lb n="0240a06" ed="T"/><l>滿之以諸穀，</l><l>是身為若此。</l>
<lb n="0240a07" ed="T"/><l>以進若干<note n="0240001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腑＝腐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腑＝腐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240001"><lem wit="【大】">腑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腐</rdg></app>，</l><l>毛髮與爪齒，</l>
<lb n="0240a08" ed="T"/><l>塵埃亦皮革，</l><l>骨節亦骨髓，</l>
<lb n="0240a09" ed="T"/><l>為凡筋與脈，</l><l>胃與心亦脾，</l>
<lb n="0240a10" ed="T"/><l>大腸亦小腸，</l><l>肝與肺亦腎，</l>
<lb n="0240a11" ed="T"/><l>脂<note n="0240002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𦠻＝𦙽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𦠻＝𦙽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240002"><lem wit="【大】">𦠻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">𦙽</rdg></app>亦大便，</l><l>淚與唾亦<note n="0240003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汗＝污【三】</note><note n="0240003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汗＝污【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0240003"><lem wit="【大】">汗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">污</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0240a12" ed="T"/><l>鼻涕膏亦血，</l><l>寒熱肪小便，</l>
<lb n="0240a13" ed="T"/><l><note n="0240004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text"><g ref="#CB02965"/>＝腦【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0240004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02965"/>＝腦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0240004"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB02965"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腦</rdg></app>之與<app type="star" corresp="#0240004"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB02965"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腦</rdg></app>膜，</l><l>皆以沈沒彼，</l>
<lb n="0240a14" ed="T"/><l>如泥塗老牛，</l><l>如其成不知。</l>
<lb n="0240a15" ed="T"/><l>身之內與外，</l><l>夫城骨與牆，</l>
<lb n="0240a16" ed="T"/><l>肉血為塗嚴，</l><l>為怨所破壞。</l>
<lb n="0240a17" ed="T"/><l>恒為以內外，</l><l>彼<note n="0240005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">央＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">央＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240005"><lem wit="【大】">央</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>若<note n="0240006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">干＝千【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240006"><lem wit="【大】">干</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">千</rdg></app>百，</l>
<lb n="0240a18" ed="T"/><l>以為貪其肉，</l><l>其外亦災害，</l>
<lb n="0240a19" ed="T"/><l>皆以多尤彼，</l><l>斯身腐敗壞。</l>
<lb n="0240a20" ed="T"/><l>譬如久故城，</l><l>晝夜供<note n="0240007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝待【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍＝待【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240007"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">待</rdg></app>之，</l>
<lb n="0240a21" ed="T"/><l>壞如已復壞，</l><l>如坎與空聚；</l>
<lb n="0240a22" ed="T"/><l>恒盜賊俱止，</l><l>取之欺殆人，</l>
<lb n="0240a23" ed="T"/><l>身為毒虺穴，</l><l>夫毒虺劇毒；</l>
<lb n="0240a24" ed="T"/><l>恒于身居止，</l><l>喜怒<note n="0240008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毒＝恚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毒＝恚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240008"><lem wit="【大】">毒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恚</rdg></app>奸<note n="0240009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弊＝蔽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弊＝蔽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240009"><lem wit="【大】">弊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蔽</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0240a25" ed="T"/><l>孚不和大毒。</l><l>正使滿百歲，</l>
<lb n="0240a26" ed="T"/><l>恒以和安隱，</l><l>忿則無<note n="0240010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240010"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">返</rdg></app>復，</l>
<lb n="0240a27" ed="T"/><l>須臾<note n="0240011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝頃【宮】</note><app n="0240011"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">頃</rdg></app>不安。</l><l>斯身為災禍，</l>
<lb n="0240a28" ed="T"/><l>嫌而有恐畏，</l><l>如虎遊荒澤，</l>
<lb n="0240a29" ed="T"/><l>有畏多恐怖。</l><l>諸念為以仰，</l>
<pb n="0240b" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0240b"/>
<lb n="0240b01" ed="T"/><l>為一切苦器，</l><l>亦為諸劇事。</l>
<lb n="0240b02" ed="T"/><l>斯身主為受，</l><l>沈於苦之法，</l>
<lb n="0240b03" ed="T"/><l>一切諸病宅，</l><l>為老死之法。</l>
<lb n="0240b04" ed="T"/><l>身為增恩愛，</l><l>苦以寒與熱，</l>
<lb n="0240b05" ed="T"/><l>或風而不和，</l><l>是則病<note n="0240012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝始【明】</note><app n="0240012"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">始</rdg></app>生。</l>
<lb n="0240b06" ed="T"/><l>為敗壞諸根，</l><l><note n="0240013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失＝夫【元】【明】</note><app n="0240013"><lem wit="【大】">失</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">夫</rdg></app>疾賊害人，</l>
<lb n="0240b07" ed="T"/><l>老死笮厄人，</l><l>如雪聚得火，</l>
<lb n="0240b08" ed="T"/><l>疾而為解釋。</l><l>斯若此無數，</l>
<lb n="0240b09" ed="T"/><l>身之多災禍，</l><l>吾所演一切，</l>
<lb n="0240b10" ed="T"/><l>未能已備具。</l><l>要以為諸苦，</l>
<lb n="0240b11" ed="T"/><l>腐身為不實，</l><l>多因緣以成，</l>
<lb n="0240b12" ed="T"/><l>大<note n="0240014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＝邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240014"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>以為<note n="0240015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>軀。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0240b13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><app type="star" corresp="#0239002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0240016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0240016"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">經一卷</rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0240b14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><head>十一因緣章</head>
<lb n="0240b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT15p0240b1501">佛言：「行者有十一因緣，滅道制令<note n="0240017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝入【宋】</note><app n="0240017"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">入</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0240b16" ed="T"/>墮<note n="0240018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惡〕－【宮】</note><app n="0240018"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>道，當不識者，謂萬物。一為大會，謂
<lb n="0240b17" ed="T"/>人眾；二者多食，謂諸美，亦謂過飽；三者為
<lb n="0240b18" ed="T"/>多行，謂多業；四為多<note n="0240019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喧〕－【宮】</note><app n="0240019"><lem wit="【大】">喧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，謂多語；五為多
<lb n="0240b19" ed="T"/>睡眠；六為會聚，謂禪中；七為習行，謂多事；
<lb n="0240b20" ed="T"/>八為愛身；九為輕，謂非法語；十為貪，謂多
<lb n="0240b21" ed="T"/>欲；十一為不好善處居，謂惡人中。行道者
<lb n="0240b22" ed="T"/>當斷是十一因緣，得道疾。」</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>